I"F<h1 id="training-courses">Training courses</h1>

<p>There are a number of training courses available. Some are free but others include a fee.</p>

<p>The <a href="http://www.plainenglish.co.uk/services/training/online-courses-available.html">Plain English campaign</a> offers online courses on using plain English and writing for websites.</p>

<p>The User-Centred Design Community runs <a href="https://designnotes.blog.gov.uk/events-and-training-in-the-user-centred-design-community/">events and training for content designers and user researchers</a>. Most are free and open to local government employees.</p>

<p>You can also find content design Bootcamps on Eventbrite throughout the year. Most of the time they include a fee. <a href="https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/">Visit Eventbrite</a> to see when the next training course is.</p>
